556
00:26:32,210 --> 00:26:37,960
♪ It will bloom in the future ♪

557
00:26:38,670 --> 00:26:41,970
♪ Time flies ♪

558
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:51,400
To commend all the villagers

559
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:54,680
for their righteous act of fighting the tomb raiders,

560
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:56,000
in addition to this banner,

561
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:59,030
the Municipal Cultural Heritage Bureau has specially made a batch of

562
00:26:59,030 --> 00:27:01,450
plaques for exemplary cultural heritage protection families

563
00:27:01,450 --> 00:27:04,960
to be awarded to every villager who participated in the action.

564
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,680
Great!

565
00:27:08,850 --> 00:27:12,250
[Exemplary Cultural Heritage Protection Family]

566
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:13,520
Slow down.

567
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:15,000
Nail it firmly, okay?

568
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:15,790
Okay, okay, okay.

569
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:17,110
Thank you, thank you.

570
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:18,020
-Yes, yes, yes.
-It's a cultural heritage protection family...

571
00:27:18,020 --> 00:27:18,880
Everybody should learn from this.

572
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:19,810
Uncle Youliang.

573
00:27:23,030 --> 00:27:23,610
Captain Yang.

574
00:27:23,610 --> 00:27:24,140
Xiaoman.

575
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:25,850
Why are you here?

576
00:27:26,550 --> 00:27:28,400
How's your dad's injury?

577
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:30,050
It's mostly healed.

578
00:27:31,030 --> 00:27:34,890
Then why didn't you go to the village committee to receive the banner?

579
00:27:36,190 --> 00:27:36,600
Uncle.

580
00:27:36,630 --> 00:27:37,430
Captain Yang.

581
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:38,890
Why are you here?

582
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:40,510
Couldn't get you to come out, so

583
00:27:40,510 --> 00:27:43,170
I came to provide door-to-door service myself.

584
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:43,730
Come.

585
00:27:44,350 --> 00:27:44,680
Okay.

586
00:27:45,070 --> 00:27:45,830
Uncle, look.

587
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:47,760
Where should we nail this plaque

588
00:27:47,860 --> 00:27:49,860
to nail away the worry in your heart?

589
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:53,590
I don't deserve this.

590
00:27:53,590 --> 00:27:55,160
I haven't made any contribution.

591
00:27:55,160 --> 00:27:56,920
How can you say you haven't contributed?

592
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:59,320
If you hadn't taken that shovel to the head,

593
00:27:59,510 --> 00:28:01,440
how would the tomb raiders have been discovered?

594
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:03,370
Yours was a contribution of blood.

595
00:28:04,110 --> 00:28:05,270
Come, let me see.

596
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:08,650
Where's a good place to nail it?

597
00:28:12,110 --> 00:28:12,830
A bit higher.

598
00:28:12,830 --> 00:28:13,560
Is this okay?

599
00:28:13,590 --> 00:28:14,160
Is it alright?

600
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:14,760
It's fine.

601
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:15,380
Come on.

602
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:16,680
Good, nail it, good.

603
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:18,480
It looks beautiful.

604
00:28:19,350 --> 00:28:20,770
Come, come, come. Nail it, let's nail it.

605
00:28:20,770 --> 00:28:21,350
A little to the right.

606
00:28:21,350 --> 00:28:21,960
That's it.

607
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:23,240
Right here?

608
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:24,130
Yes, that's good.

609
00:28:24,130 --> 00:28:25,660
Okay? Come on, here you are.

610
00:28:28,240 --> 00:28:29,770
Alright, I'll be going now.

611
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:32,680
Luo Qing from the archaeological team asked me to go and mobilize

612
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,920
to form a cultural heritage protection team in the village.

613
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:37,030
No one's responding, so I'll go and see to it myself.

614
00:28:37,030 --> 00:28:37,830
A little more.

615
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:39,030
I'm leaving.

616
00:28:39,030 --> 00:28:39,960
Come by anytime.

617
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:40,290
Okay.

618
00:28:40,350 --> 00:28:41,240
Take care, Captain Yang.

619
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:41,770
Alright.

620
00:28:42,110 --> 00:28:43,240
You two nail it well.

621
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:43,570
Okay.

622
00:28:45,270 --> 00:28:46,510
Looks great.

623
00:28:53,070 --> 00:28:53,870
Captain Yang,

624
00:28:54,270 --> 00:28:55,400
how's the recruitment going?

625
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:57,330
When I was nailing the door plates,

626
00:28:57,680 --> 00:28:59,850
I asked for opinions from each household.

627
00:28:59,850 --> 00:29:01,580
Some were quite enthusiastic,

628
00:29:02,070 --> 00:29:03,730
but there were some concerns.

629
00:29:04,310 --> 00:29:06,160
After all, they're afraid of not being able to fight against the tomb raiders.

630
00:29:06,160 --> 00:29:07,880
And they don't want to lose their own labor force.

631
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:09,640
If they're going to do it, just do it. If not, forget it.

632
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:12,300
I don't see anyone here who really wants to do it.

633
00:29:12,510 --> 00:29:13,240
Otherwise, how about this:

634
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:14,070
when Fang Kun wakes up,

635
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:16,070
I'll patrol with him. We don't need them.

636
00:29:16,070 --> 00:29:16,930
Uncle Shoucun,

637
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:18,270
we have such a large area,

638
00:29:18,270 --> 00:29:20,070
how can just two people guard it?

639
00:29:20,350 --> 00:29:22,210
I can understand their concerns.

640
00:29:22,270 --> 00:29:23,880
The farmers are very busy every day,

641
00:29:23,880 --> 00:29:26,150
and they won't have time if they join the cultural heritage protection team.

642
00:29:26,150 --> 00:29:28,550
Here's the case. I've submitted an application to the higher-ups

643
00:29:28,550 --> 00:29:30,830
to allocate a portion of our archaeological funds

644
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:31,650
as a reward.

645
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:33,590
We'll provide some subsidies for our cultural heritage protection team.

646
00:29:33,590 --> 00:29:35,150
Let's establish this first.

647
00:29:35,150 --> 00:29:37,420
It's perfect timing as we haven't defined the cultural heritage protection area yet.

648
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:38,750
Let's start dealing with it now.

649
00:29:38,750 --> 00:29:41,010
This way, the work can proceed smoothly.

650
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,030
Your concerns are valid.

651
00:29:43,030 --> 00:29:44,880
I'll also apply to the bureau when I get back,

652
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:46,400
to see if we can get some funds allocated

653
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:48,240
to build up our cultural heritage protection team.

654
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:48,680
Okay.

655
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:50,900
Secretary.

656
00:29:51,110 --> 00:29:53,550
Could you please inform all the villagers about this?

657
00:29:53,550 --> 00:29:55,750
Let's gather enough people as soon as possible.

658
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:56,550
It can be done.

659
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:58,400
However, in the past,

660
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,030
it was always the Chief who handled these things.

661
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,350
The villagers all listened to him.

662
00:30:01,350 --> 00:30:03,010
Now he's lost his enthusiasm.

663
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,960
So this matter has become a bit troublesome.

664
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:07,790
No one in our village is as influential as he is.

665
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:08,800
That's right.

666
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:12,030
Uncle.

667
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:12,960
Uncle Youliang.

668
00:30:13,550 --> 00:30:14,150
Youliang.

669
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:16,160
In our Yin Village's territory,

670
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:18,090
could there be shortage of people?

671
00:30:18,790 --> 00:30:19,320
Captain.

672
00:30:19,910 --> 00:30:21,110
How do you want to arrange this?

673
00:30:21,110 --> 00:30:21,640
Are these

674
00:30:22,270 --> 00:30:23,200
people enough?

675
00:30:24,810 --> 00:30:25,540
It's enough.

676
00:30:26,030 --> 00:30:26,590
Enough.

677
00:30:29,870 --> 00:30:31,000
Fellow countrymen!

678
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:32,940
You've all seen it, right?

679
00:30:33,070 --> 00:30:34,640
These thieves with their probing rods

680
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:36,770
have turned our land into a honeycomb.

681
00:30:37,050 --> 00:30:38,880
Not only can we no longer irrigate our land,

682
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:40,160
but most importantly, this group

683
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:43,310
has almost pierced through our ancestors' coffin boards.

684
00:30:43,310 --> 00:30:44,840
Can we allow this to happen?

685
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:45,920
No, we can't.

686
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:49,240
If we can't allow it, then let's deal with them.

687
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:52,110
The Chief still has strong leadership.

688
00:30:52,110 --> 00:30:52,710
By the way,

689
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:54,510
there's another matter today.

690
00:30:54,510 --> 00:30:56,880
Our cultural heritage protection team needs a captain.

691
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,920
Who do you think is suitable?

692
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:04,160
I think Youliang is suitable for this.

693
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:05,450
I disagree.

694
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:08,240
I've been working in cultural heritage protection the longest.

695
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,240
I have the most experience.

696
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:11,310
If we're choosing a captain, it should definitely be me.

697
00:31:11,310 --> 00:31:12,830
Youliang is good at production,

698
00:31:12,830 --> 00:31:14,350
but he doesn't understand cultural heritage protection.

699
00:31:14,350 --> 00:31:14,950
Moreover,

700
00:31:15,070 --> 00:31:16,590
we can't let a thief's father

701
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:17,330
be the captain of the cultural heritage protection team.

702
00:31:17,330 --> 00:31:17,790
Right, right, right.

703
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:18,680
People will laugh at us.

704
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:19,830
You do it, you do it. I can't do it.

705
00:31:19,830 --> 00:31:20,960
Uncle Youliang, Uncle Youliang.

706
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:21,510
What are you saying?

707
00:31:21,510 --> 00:31:21,960
Alright, alright.

708
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,160
What's a tomb raider anyway?

709
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:23,790
Don't worry about it.

710
00:31:23,790 --> 00:31:24,720
Chief, Chief, don't leave.

711
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:25,700
Chief, don't leave.

712
00:31:25,700 --> 00:31:27,830
You're the most suitable to be the captain.

713
00:31:27,830 --> 00:31:29,240
Don't you all agree?

714
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:30,590
Yes.

715
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:35,110
Cultural heritage protection is just patrolling, right?

716
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:36,400
Just these areas in the village,

717
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:37,350
who in our village

718
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:41,150
couldn't walk through with their eyes closed without getting lost?

719
00:31:41,310 --> 00:31:42,880
I also think Youliang is suitable.

720
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:44,270
If he becomes the captain,

721
00:31:44,270 --> 00:31:45,130
I'll accept it.

722
00:31:45,270 --> 00:31:46,920
I accept too, I accept too.

723
00:31:46,940 --> 00:31:47,600
That works.

724
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,330
Uncle Youliang,

725
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:50,430
the cultural heritage protection team

726
00:31:50,430 --> 00:31:51,690
is counting on you now.

727
00:31:52,790 --> 00:31:53,590
Alright then.

728
00:31:56,110 --> 00:31:56,830
I'll do it.

729
00:31:57,750 --> 00:31:58,750
Did you hear that?

730
00:32:00,350 --> 00:32:01,880
Did you hear what they said?

731
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:02,830
Fine.

732
00:32:04,510 --> 00:32:04,920
Fine.

733
00:32:06,790 --> 00:32:07,720
Here's the case.

734
00:32:08,310 --> 00:32:09,910
Let Fang Kun know about this.

735
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:11,310
When he has recovered,

736
00:32:11,310 --> 00:32:12,200
tell him to come back quickly.

737
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:13,600
I've made a room for him.

738
00:32:13,710 --> 00:32:14,240
Alright.

739
00:32:14,270 --> 00:32:17,000
We welcome the archaeological team back anytime.

740
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:17,550
Okay.

741
00:32:17,830 --> 00:32:18,430
Youliang!

742
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,270
Take care, Uncle Youliang.

743
00:32:21,270 --> 00:32:21,880
Mrs. Zan,

744
00:32:22,530 --> 00:32:23,390
how is it going?

745
00:32:24,200 --> 00:32:24,860
He's awake?

746
00:32:27,030 --> 00:32:27,630
Over here.

747
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:29,540
Uncle, Auntie,

748
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:31,610
Luo Qing, you're here.

749
00:32:36,510 --> 00:32:37,110
This is...

750
00:32:37,550 --> 00:32:38,680
He just fell asleep.

751
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:43,240
Sis,

752
00:32:44,590 --> 00:32:45,920
what did the doctor say?

753
00:32:47,070 --> 00:32:49,010
The doctor said there are aftereffects.

754
00:32:49,010 --> 00:32:51,670
It has affected his speech and motor functions.

755
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:53,020
Can he recover?

756
00:32:57,350 --> 00:32:58,280
It's hard to say.

757
00:33:08,750 --> 00:33:09,410
He's awake.

758
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:12,680
Kun.

759
00:33:13,160 --> 00:33:13,590
Kun.

760
00:33:24,510 --> 00:33:25,420
He finally woke up.

761
00:33:25,420 --> 00:33:27,550
You all stay here and keep him company.

762
00:33:27,760 --> 00:33:28,230
Mom.

763
00:33:44,660 --> 00:33:46,550
Who are

764
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:47,680
you?

765
00:33:48,750 --> 00:33:49,610
What did he say?

766
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:51,270
He asked who I am.

767
00:33:55,790 --> 00:33:56,240
You...

768
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,290
Stop scaring us, will you?

769
00:33:59,960 --> 00:34:01,360
You just had a good sleep.

770
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:03,660
You have no idea what we've been through.

771
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:05,040
I mean, you...

772
00:34:05,350 --> 00:34:06,310
You sent us away

773
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:09,760
and ran off to the site to play hero and catch tomb raiders.

774
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:11,360
Why did you have to be so cool?

775
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:14,570
Back then...

776
00:34:15,070 --> 00:34:17,469
I shouldn't have left you alone at the site.

777
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:19,540
You really scared us to death.

778
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:21,510
You really almost scared us to death.

779
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:22,440
Do you know that?

780
00:34:24,460 --> 00:34:26,670
Why do you have to learn everything from Zan?

781
00:34:26,670 --> 00:34:29,110
Learn the good things, not the bad ones, okay?

782
00:34:29,110 --> 00:34:29,960
Are you silly?

783
00:34:30,800 --> 00:34:32,469
Don't do this again in the future.

784
00:34:32,469 --> 00:34:33,070
Exactly.

785
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:36,760
What?

786
00:34:37,400 --> 00:34:38,590
I'm fine.

787
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:40,040
What?

788
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:41,530
You're being tough.

789
00:34:41,590 --> 00:34:42,590
He says he's fine.

790
00:34:43,639 --> 00:34:44,920
Of course he can't be in trouble.

791
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:47,520
What would you do if something happened to him?

792
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:53,600
Oh, right. I have some good news for you.

793
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:57,760
The archaeological project in Yin Village has been confirmed.

794
00:34:57,760 --> 00:35:00,220
The provincial institute will be in charge.

795
00:35:00,530 --> 00:35:01,530
Are you happy now?

796
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:04,210
Do you know who's leading the team?

797
00:35:13,510 --> 00:35:14,910
Why are you looking at me?

798
00:35:15,510 --> 00:35:16,970
Don't you trust me to lead?

799
00:35:24,070 --> 00:35:26,920
I've already handed over the Lv Family Tomb project.

800
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:28,780
Someone else will take care of it.

801
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:31,510
Once this project is completed,

802
00:35:31,510 --> 00:35:33,110
you'll be eligible for a researcher position.

803
00:35:33,110 --> 00:35:34,030
Giving up now

804
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,510
is really a shame.

805
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:39,030
Fang Kun,

806
00:35:39,690 --> 00:35:41,820
Luo Qing has made such a big sacrifice.

807
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:43,750
You should also do your best.

808
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:45,630
Don't do foolish things in the future.

809
00:35:45,630 --> 00:35:47,290
Take good care of your health.

810
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:49,090
Come back soon to help Luo Qing.

811
00:35:49,110 --> 00:35:49,840
Understand?

812
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,800
Mrs. Zan, you've said it all.

813
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:53,110
What's left for him to say?

814
00:35:53,110 --> 00:35:54,630
What's so great about being a researcher?

815
00:35:54,630 --> 00:35:56,110
It's just a few hundred yuan more, isn't it?

816
00:35:56,110 --> 00:35:57,590
When Fang Kun gets better,

817
00:35:57,590 --> 00:35:59,390
he can make it up to you, can't he?

818
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:01,800
Who is he to me that he needs to make up for anything?

819
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:02,760
Right, right, right.

820
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:04,490
It's all yours, it's all yours.

821
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:06,800
Alright, stop fooling around.

822
00:36:09,730 --> 00:36:11,730
When will your city office be ready?

823
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,140
Ready for what?

824
00:36:13,150 --> 00:36:14,630
Didn't Director Zhang tell you?

825
00:36:14,630 --> 00:36:15,360
Tell us what?

826
00:36:16,270 --> 00:36:18,760
The grand tomb in Yin Village was first discovered by your team.

827
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:20,190
You've put in a lot of effort.

828
00:36:20,190 --> 00:36:22,550
You and Fang Kun are the most familiar with Yin Village.

829
00:36:22,550 --> 00:36:25,070
You've also accumulated a wealth of relevant preparations.

830
00:36:25,070 --> 00:36:25,960
So it's been decided this time

831
00:36:25,960 --> 00:36:28,960
that the two units will jointly form a combined archaeological team.

832
00:36:28,960 --> 00:36:31,000
The National Cultural Heritage Administration has already approved it.

833
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,860
However, I'll be the team leader.

834
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:34,850
So you two will have to listen to me.

